sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: Potentially Suspicious DLL Registered Via Odbcconf.EXE
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects execution of "odbcconf" with the "REGSVR" action where the DLL in question doesn't contain a ".dll" extension. Which is often used as a method to evade defenses.
